An-10A Ukraina (Cat)
Entered service with Aeroflot in the autumn of 1959. Carries between 80-130 passengers depending on internal configuration. Recommended cruising speed, 370mph at 26,250ft.
Dimensions: Span 124ft; length 121ft; height 32ft; wing area, 1293 sq ft.
